divs: Sighting DetailsMy friends and I were at McDonalds Drive thru, I looked up, saw a plane with a trail coming from it and a few inches (because it was pretty far away from us in the sky) we saw a translucent orb ascending into the sky. After about one minute of viewing it disappeared. Looked nothing like the plane close by. We were facing east, we saw the sphere in about an ESE direction.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Moorhead
There were no other sightings in Moorhead on or around December 23rd 2011
Summary: silverish white orb ascending near plane then disappeared within two minutes
